---

## About Joshna Fernando

**Birth & Family Background**

* Born on **12 November 1991** in **London**, Joshna comes from an influential Tamil film family. Her mother, **Saroja**, acted in iconic films like *Maro Charitra* (1978) and *Vadamalai* (1982), while her father, **Stanley Fernando**, is related to noted actress–producer **Radhika** and actress **Nirosha**, making Joshna their cousin ([Wikipedia][1], [Veethi][2]).

---

## Early Career & Acting Highlights

* **Tele-film Debut (1999)**: At just four years old, she debuted portraying Vikram’s character’s daughter in Radhika Sarathkumar’s tele-film *Siragugal* ([Wikipedia][1], [Veethi][2]).

* **Adult Film Career in Tamil Cinema**:

  * **Marupadiyum Oru Kadhal** (2012): Played Maheswari, a London-based medical student in this romance; the film faced negative reviews and underwhelming box-office performance ([Wikipedia][1]).
  * **Kai** (2012): Co-starred in this romantic-action drama, again met with poor reception ([Wikipedia][1]).
  * **Irumbu Kuthirai** (2014): Joined the cast after another actress exited; her scenes were largely edited out after the original actress returned. A brief appearance remained, reimagined as the character’s sister in a biking warehouse sequence ([Wikipedia][1]).

* **Other Projects**:

  * Acted alongside music legend Ilayaraja in *Naadi Thudikuthadi*, a Fiji-sponsored tourism film that unfortunately was never released due to production issues ([Wikipedia][1]).
  * Was attached to *Parthom Pazhaginom*, directed by Rasu Madhuravan; but the project was shelved following the director’s passing ([Wikipedia][1]).
  * Also involved in *Manam Nilluna Nikkadhadi*, completed but unreleased ([Everything Explained Today][3], [Wiki2][4]).

---

## Pageantry & Later Work

* **Miss Sri Lanka Contestant (2013)**: As the only British national, Joshna was a finalist in the Veet Miss Sri Lanka beauty pageant ([Wikipedia][1]).

* **Adult Modeling**: She currently works in the adult modeling industry and is reportedly the **first Tamil actress officially signed by Playboy** ([Wikipedia][1], [Everything Explained Today][3]).

---

Here’s an official portrait of **Meghna Alam**, a prominent Bangladeshi beauty queen and environmental advocate.

---

## Profile: Meghna Alam – Former Beauty Queen & Activist

### Pageant Achievements & Leadership Roles

* Crowned **Miss Earth Bangladesh 2020**, becoming the inaugural representative from the country at the international Miss Earth pageant.([Wikipedia][1])
* Competed in **Miss Universe Bangladesh 2019**, placing in the top 18, and **Miss World Bangladesh 2023**, reaching the top 20.([Wikipedia][1])
* Serves as **Chairperson of the Miss Bangladesh Organization** and is a **founder of the Miss Bangladesh Foundation** (formerly Ekottro Foundation), positioning herself as a leading figure in Bangladesh’s pageant circuit.([Wikipedia][1])

### Advocacy & Social Work

* Established the **Ekottro Foundation**, aimed at empowering youth through themes like sustainability, women’s leadership, and climate awareness.([The Statesman][2])
* Actively engaged in social activism from a young age and holds certifications in political leadership training from esteemed institutions.

---

## Legal Controversy & Diplomatic Fallout

### Arrest and Charges

In **April 2025**, Meghna Alam was **detained under Bangladesh's Special Powers Act**, which permits preventive detention. Authorities accused her of jeopardizing diplomatic relations and potentially harming national interests.([Wikipedia][1], [www.ndtv.com][3])

### The Alleged Trigger

Reports indicate that Meghna had publicly claimed to be in a personal relationship with a **Saudi Arabian diplomat** stationed in Dhaka. According to her father, she ended the relationship upon discovering he was already married with children—a situation that allegedly prompted backlash leading to her detention.([The Statesman][2], [Femina][4])

### Public & Legal Response

The manner and terms of her arrest sparked widespread criticism from human rights groups such as **Amnesty International**, who called for either the formal filing of charges or her release.([Femina][4], [The Siasat Daily][5])
Events unfolded dramatically when Meghna was taken into custody during a **live Facebook broadcast**, causing significant public alarm.([The Statesman][2], [Aaj Tak বাংলা][6])
Authorities have since **detained her for 30 days**, but doubts linger about whether due process was properly followed.([The Statesman][2], [punjabkesari][7])

---

| ---------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------------------ |
| **Title**        | Miss Earth Bangladesh 2020                                               |

| **Social Focus** | Environmentalism, women’s leadership, youth empowerment                  |

### Who Is Trisha Kar Madhu?

**Trisha Kar Madhu** (sometimes referred to as Madhu or real name possibly Trisha Khan) is an Indian actress, model, and content creator active in the **Bhojpuri film industry**.

#### Personal Details & Background:

* **Birth**: Born on **2 September 1994** in **Konnagar, Kolkata, West Bengal**, and from a Bengali Hindu family.([bhojpuripro.com][1], [The Wiki][2], [hindijankaripur][3])

Debuted on the small screen with the Bhojpuri serial *Ham Hai Hindustani* and later transitioned into films and music videos.([bhojpuripro.com][1], [hindijankaripur][3], [The Wiki][2])

* **Popular Engagements**:

  * Featured in Bhojpuri music hits like *Raja Tani Jai Na Bhaariya* and *Laika Tohre Ke Papa Kahta*, which elevated her visibility.([hindijankaripur][3], [SheThePeople][6])

Certainly! Here's a comprehensive biography of **Roshmi Banik**, an Indian actress and entrepreneur:

---

## 🧿 Roshmi Banik – Biography

### 📅 Personal Details

* **Full Name**: Roshmi Banik
* **Date of Birth**: March 9, 1992 (Age: 33)
* **Place of Birth**: Kolkata, West Bengal, India
* **Nationality**: Indian
* **Ethnicity**: Bengali
* **Religion**: Hindu
* **Education**: Bachelor of Business Administration (BBA) from Shri Shikshayatan College, Kolkata
* **Languages**: Fluent in English, Hindi, and Bengali ([Big Brother Wiki][1], [Booking Agent Info][2], [Facebook][3], [The Indian Express][4], [India Forums][5])

---

### 🎭 Career Highlights

* **Television**: Roshmi gained prominence as a contestant on **Bigg Boss 12** (2018), where she entered as part of a "jodi" with Mital Joshi. Following Mital's early eviction, Roshmi partnered with Kriti Verma and was eventually evicted after 14 days in the house .([StarsUnfolded][6])

* **Acting Roles**: She has appeared in several television and short film projects, including:

  * **Ishq Aaj Kal** (2019)
  * **Venganza** (2021)
  * **Wanna Have Good Time 2** (2019)
  * **Step In** (2021) 

---

### 👜 Entrepreneurial Ventures

* **EL CUERO FASHIONS LLP**: Roshmi is the co-founder and designated partner of EL CUERO FASHIONS, a Kolkata-based company specializing in premium leather goods .([LinkedIn][7])

* **Other Business Interests**: She is also associated with **Furze Dealers Private Limited** and **Banik Ace Ventures Private Limited**, indicating her active involvement in the business sector .([IndiaFilings][8])

---

### 📱 Social Media Presence

* **Instagram**: [@roshmibanik](https://www.instagram.com/roshmibanik/), with over 775K followers, where she shares lifestyle, fashion, and personal content.
* **Email**: [roshmiofficial@gmail.com](mailto:roshmiofficial@gmail.com)([Instagram][9])

---

### 💡 Personal Insights

* **Hobbies**: Singing, shopping, and traveling 
* **Favorite Cuisine**: Italian
* **Favorite TV Show**: Bigg Boss
* **Dream Destination**: Miami
* **Favorite Actor**: Ranbir Kapoor
* **Favorite Actress**: Priyanka Chopra
* **Favorite Color**: Red ([India Forums][5], [Big Brother Wiki][1], [Famous Birthdays][10])

data.description:
[![imdb.com/name/nm9389735](https://images.openai.com/thumbnails/url/9EuOz3icu1mSUVJSUGylr5-al1xUWVCSmqJbkpRnoJdeXJJYkpmsl5yfq5-Zm5ieWmxfaAuUsXL0S7F0Tw4qzM_0zfEtMs8Lyg0PS_b2cXQO8HE0sKhKLTUpNtX1dM9KLPUvDynPLPSwMMg0CEny9PfILUvOqvAoDVQrBgAhISol)](https://www.imdb.com/name/nm9389735/?utm_source=chatgpt.com)

**Aisha Ahmed** is an Indian actress and voice-over artist, born on **May 8, 1996**, in **Mumbai, Maharashtra**. She is the daughter of actress **Rukhsar Rehman** and filmmaker **Faruk Kabir** .([Golden][1], [StarsUnfolded][2])

---

### 🎬 Career Highlights

Aisha began her acting career with a minor role in the film **Tum Bin 2** (2016). She gained recognition for her performances in the film **3 Storeys** (2018) and the web series **Adulting** (2018), where she portrayed Nikhat Rizvi . She also starred in the romantic comedy **Minus One** (2019) and its sequel, **Minus One: New Chapter** (2023) . In 2021, she featured in the MX Player series **Balcony Buddies** and the short film **Clean** . In 2022, she appeared in the film **Kacchey Limbu** . In 2024, she starred in the music video **"Nadaaniyan"** alongside singer Akshath Acharya .([Wikipedia][3])

---

### 🧬 Personal Life

Aisha was raised by her mother, Rukhsar Rehman, and spent her childhood under the care of her grandparents in Rampur. She has openly discussed her upbringing and the influence of strong women in her life on platforms like HealthShots . As of 2022, she has been reported to be in a relationship with marketing professional **Uday Oberoi**, though neither has publicly confirmed this .([Healthshots][4], [Wikipedia][3])

---

### 📺 Web Series & Films

| ---- | ------------------------ | ------------- | ------------------------------------ |
| 2016 | Tum Bin 2                | -             |                                      |

| 2022 | Kacchey Limbu            | Sara          |                                      |
| 2024 | Nadaaniyan (Music Video) | -             | ([StarsUnfolded][2], [Wikipedia][3]) |

---

### 📸 Social Media & Influence

Aisha is active on Instagram under the handle [@aisharahmed](https://www.instagram.com/aisharahmed/), where she shares lifestyle content, fashion posts, and personal insights. With over 900K followers, she engages her audience through relatable content and humor .([Instagram][5], [Whosthat 360][6])
